high_descs: Turn around, go straight past the center table, turn right after the table, go to the counter past the stove on the left.
Pick up the spoon on the counter, the one closer to the plate.
Bring the spoon to the sink on the right.
Wash the spoon in the sink with water.
Bring the cleaned spoon to the left side of the table behind you.
Stand the spoon on the table, in front of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Stand a cleaned spoon on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go forward, then turn right to go around the kitchen island, go towards the coffee maker, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the leftmost spoon on the counter.
Turn around and go forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Clean the spoon in the sink.
Turn around and go toward the kitchen island, then turn left and move forward, then turn right and walk along the kitchen island, then turn right to face the kitchen island.
Put the spoon on the kitchen island.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the shelves then turn right and walk to the counter then turn left.
Pick up the spoon that's closest to you on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink then turn left to face it.
Wash the spoon in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and walk to the counter then step to your left and walk to the stool then turn right.
Put the spoon on the potato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon on the counter.
